originalText.text: We had the pleasure of working with Charlie Kickham from Cayenne Consulting for our startup's business plan and financial model. From the very beginning, Charlie demonstrated a remarkable understanding of our vision and business purpose, asking us thought-provoking questions during the data gathering sessions. His availability and willingness to address any queries were exceptional, and his insights proved to be invaluable. The business plan and financial model he delivered were outstanding - meticulously detailed and comprehensive. Thanks to Charlie's expertise, we received numerous compliments from potential investors, truly appreciating the level of professionalism and insight evident in his work.

originalText.text:
Working with Cayenne Consulting has been a joy not only due to their high level of professionalism, but also because of their personal and relatable approach. Their enthusiasm and interest in my project made our interactions a truly enjoyable experience, which is very important when embarking on a new venture that can bring forth a lot of anxiety and uncertainty. Their explanations and breakdown of the plan were presented in a highly succinct manner, allowing a person like myself to comprehend and absorb the information more fully.

I strongly recommend using their services, and would not hesitate to work with them again in the near future!

Cayenne Consulting completely knocked it out of the park! The detail in the financials was beyond what I ever expected. The amount of research into the area and demographic was amazing! I cannot say enough about this team. Communication was so seamless. They absolutely know what they’re doing!
I am very grateful for the effort, research, and insight that Cayenne Consulting devoted to my dream.
